org.appkit.measure
Class Measurement

java.lang.Object
  org.appkit.measure.Measurement

public final class Measurement
extends Object

This static class starts, keeps track of and stops measurement. Measurement can be nested, the internal state is managed using ThreadLocal variables. Every method has a boolean switch to turn off measurement, so it can be kept in the code and turned of for performance reasons.
